%95/poem--BAofQiJEK-wylfgkTnWBg">Tô đài lãm cổ - 蘇台覽古</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/author-8WYDeeki5xZo8eD-k6Sk5A">Lý Bạch</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%C3%A1i-Thu%E1%BA%ADn/Tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-An-xu%C3%A2n-m%E1%BB%99/poem-EfveM4kJVW--oriWHDFL-A">Trường An xuân mộ - 長安春暮</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%C3%A1i-Thu%E1%BA%ADn/author-l-NINz3JTJVTCX2aN0HlSQ">Thái Thuận</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Dung/T%E1%BB%AD-quy/poem-BZtVKAu5IOR41L5TXLK3Fw">Tử quy - 子規</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Dung/author-qoi_3MEdeZkoj0TClsekFA">Ngô Dung</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%E1%BA%A9m-Minh-Th%E1%BA%A7n/V%E1%BA%A1n-L%E1%BB%8Bch-ng%C5%A9-ni%C3%AAn-xu%C3%A2n-h%E1%BB%AFu-hi%E1%BA%BFn-ng%C5%A9-s%E1%BA%AFc-anh-v%C5%A9-gi%E1%BA%A3-chi%E1%BA%BFu-nh%E1%BA%ADp-chi-cung-ph%C3%BA-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-RS_jwXLHQDzMWUzVomaxzw">Vạn Lịch ngũ niên xuân hữu hiến ngũ sắc anh vũ giả chiếu nhập chi cung phú kỳ 2 - 萬歷五年春有獻五色鸚鵡者詔入之恭賦其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%E1%BA%A9m-Minh-Th%E1%BA%A7n/author-YaMRkwvXgT5g5W4Ryp1GKA">Thẩm Minh Thần</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Li%C3%AAn-Ho%C3%A0nh/V%E1%BB%8Bnh-s%E1%BB%AD-k%E1%BB%B3-46-V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Chi%C3%AAu-Qu%C3%A2n/poem-JAwavE2yrleTDh0pWDn7rw">Vịnh sử kỳ 46 - Vương Chiêu Quân - 詠史其四十六－王昭君</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Li%C3%AAn-Ho%C3%A0nh/author-8k5-bGU03Z_txBNZHdLGbQ">Liên Hoành</a>)<br></div>	</div>
